extends ../errorTemplate.jade
block content
  //- h1 and p elements should say whether container is building, stopped, or crashed.
  h1.h1 Container is building
  p.p The container for
    strong.strong  api/my-cool-branch
    |  is building.
  //- link goes to the relevant container in the containers view,
    - with build logs open if container is building
    - with CMD logs open if container is stopped or crashed
  a.link(
    href = "/#{ownerName}/#{instanceName}"
  ) View build logs in Runnable